{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_02_02",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 2話 遙子だけの魅力",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピースの沖縄ライブ前日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The day before the Sunny Peace Okinawa concert",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2000,
          "startTime": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなー、迎えに来たぞー\n明日のライブに備えてそろそろホテルに戻ろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ girls! I’m here to pick you up!\nLet’s head back to the hotel and get ready for the concert tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "おかしいな、ここでライブのリハーサルを\nしているはずだが、みんなどこに行ったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s odd. They should be here rehearsing.\nWhere are they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.733333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3766.6666666666674,
          "startTime": 18.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 18.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、来てたのね\nわざわざ迎えに来てもらってごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ there you are.\nSorry for making you come out to get us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 23.933333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん、お疲れ様です\n他のみんなはどこですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko. Hey.\nWhere are the others?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 28.366666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "みんなでお風呂に入ってるわ\nここのお風呂、全員で入れるくらい広いのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They went to take a bath.\nThe bath here is big enough for everyone to fit in it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 34.93333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "大事なライブ前なのに随分リラックスしてるな……\n遙子さんは一緒に入らなかったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s pretty laidback‚ with a big concert coming up.\nBut you aren’t joining them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 42.166666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "私は……なんとなく気まずくて……\nリハーサルでモヤモヤしちゃったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t really feel like it.\nI’ve been feeling a bit uneasy during rehearsals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 50.06666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "モヤモヤ？　リハーサルで何かあったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have? Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 54.56666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……ちょっと言いづらいかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s… kinda hard to talk about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 59.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "悩みがあるなら相談して下さいよ\n俺は遙子さんの力になりたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If something’s the matter‚ you can let me know.\nI want to help you however I can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 65.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよね、{user}君ならいいか……\n実は、ここだけの話だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess I can tell you‚ {user}…\nJust between us‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 74.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "今日は本番と同じステージ衣装に着替えて\nリハーサルをしたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today we were rehearsing while wearing\nthe actual costumes we’ll use for the concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "今回の衣装は水着風だから肌の露出が多いでしょ？\nだからみんなのスタイルがよく分かって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They are bikini-style‚ so they show off quite a lot of skin.\nI could see everyone’s figures‚ and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 90.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……スタイル？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Figures?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "そう……肉付き……かな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I have more… meat?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 98.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "みんな手足が細くてすらっとしているのに\n私だけむちっとしている気がしたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The others have such slender arms and legs‚\nand I felt like I was more curvy than them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "一緒にお風呂に入ってみんなを見たら\n私だけむちむちなんだと絶望しそうで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I saw what they all looked like in the bath‚\nI’m sure it would have destroyed me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 111.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、そういうことですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah. I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 114.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどじゃないわ！　これは大問題よ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean “you see”?! This is a big problem!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 118.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "ステージではみんなと並んで踊るのよ！\n嫌でも比較されちゃうんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to sing and dance alongside them on the stage!\nI’m going to be compared to them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに気にしなくても、遙子さんは素敵ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You are lovely‚ Haruko. No need to worry so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 128.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "実際に見てないからそんなことが言えるのよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can say that because you haven’t seen me in the costume!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 132.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "……いいわ。そこまで言うなら\n今から着替えてくるからちゃんと見てちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. If this is what it’s going to take‚\nI’ll go get changed! You just watch!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 138.83333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "え、遙子さん？　着替えるって……",
      "translations": {
